{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WorkerGlobalScope.importScripts()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/importScripts","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>console</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/location\"><code>location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/navigator\"><code>navigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/self\"><code>self</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/dump\"><code>dump()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>importScripts()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/languagechange_event\"><code>languagechange</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/offline_event\"><code>offline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/online_event\"><code>online</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Workers API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>importScripts()</strong></code> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a> インターフェースのメソッドで、1つ以上のスクリプトをワーカーのスコープ内に同期的に読み込みます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">importScripts</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nself<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">importScripts</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=